{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":760,"text":"When I was a kid,\nI was the quintessential nerd."},{"time":5320,"text":"I think some of you were, too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":7520,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":8760,"text":"And you, sir, who laughed the loudest,\nyou probably still are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":12000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":14280,"text":"I grew up in a small town\nin the dusty plains of north Texas,"},{"time":17800,"text":"the son of a sheriff\nwho was the son of a pastor."},{"time":21160,"text":"Getting into trouble was not an option."},{"time":24040,"text":"And so I started reading\ncalculus books for fun."}]},{"cues":[{"time":27320,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":28880,"text":"You did, too."},{"time":30600,"text":"That led me to building a laser\nand a computer and model rockets,"},{"time":34360,"text":"and that led me to making\nrocket fuel in my bedroom."},{"time":37960,"text":"Now, in scientific terms,"},{"time":41640,"text":"we call this a very bad idea."}]},{"cues":[{"time":44920,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":46160,"text":"Around that same time,"},{"time":48360,"text":"Stanley Kubrick's \"2001: A Space Odyssey\"\ncame to the theaters,"},{"time":51600,"text":"and my life was forever changed."},{"time":54280,"text":"I loved everything about that movie,"},{"time":56360,"text":"especially the HAL 9000."},{"time":58920,"text":"Now, HAL was a sentient computer"},{"time":61000,"text":"designed to guide the Discovery spacecraft"},{"time":63480,"text":"from the Earth to Jupiter."},{"time":66040,"text":"HAL was also a flawed character,"},{"time":68120,"text":"for in the end he chose\nto value the mission over human life."},{"time":72840,"text":"Now, HAL was a fictional character,"},{"time":74960,"text":"but nonetheless he speaks to our fears,"},{"time":77640,"text":"our fears of being subjugated"},{"time":79760,"text":"by some unfeeling, artificial intelligence"},{"time":82800,"text":"who is indifferent to our humanity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85880,"text":"I believe that such fears are unfounded."},{"time":88480,"text":"Indeed, we stand at a remarkable time"},{"time":91200,"text":"in human history,"},{"time":92760,"text":"where, driven by refusal to accept\nthe limits of our bodies and our minds,"},{"time":97760,"text":"we are building machines"},{"time":99480,"text":"of exquisite, beautiful\ncomplexity and grace"},{"time":103120,"text":"that will extend the human experience"},{"time":105200,"text":"in ways beyond our imagining."}]},{"cues":[{"time":107720,"text":"After a career that led me\nfrom the Air Force Academy"},{"time":110320,"text":"to Space Command to now,"},{"time":112280,"text":"I became a systems engineer,"},{"time":114000,"text":"and recently I was drawn\ninto an engineering problem"},{"time":116760,"text":"associated with NASA's mission to Mars."},{"time":119360,"text":"Now, in space flights to the Moon,"},{"time":121880,"text":"we can rely upon\nmission control in Houston"},{"time":125040,"text":"to watch over all aspects of a flight."},{"time":127040,"text":"However, Mars is 200 times further away,"},{"time":130600,"text":"and as a result it takes\non average 13 minutes"},{"time":133840,"text":"for a signal to travel\nfrom the Earth to Mars."},{"time":137000,"text":"If there's trouble,\nthere's not enough time."},{"time":140840,"text":"And so a reasonable engineering solution"},{"time":143360,"text":"calls for us to put mission control"},{"time":145960,"text":"inside the walls of the Orion spacecraft."},{"time":149000,"text":"Another fascinating idea\nin the mission profile"},{"time":151920,"text":"places humanoid robots\non the surface of Mars"},{"time":154840,"text":"before the humans themselves arrive,"},{"time":156720,"text":"first to build facilities"},{"time":158400,"text":"and later to serve as collaborative\nmembers of the science team."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163400,"text":"Now, as I looked at this\nfrom an engineering perspective,"},{"time":166160,"text":"it became very clear to me\nthat what I needed to architect"},{"time":169360,"text":"was a smart, collaborative,"},{"time":171560,"text":"socially intelligent\nartificial intelligence."},{"time":173960,"text":"In other words, I needed to build\nsomething very much like a HAL"},{"time":178280,"text":"but without the homicidal tendencies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":180720,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":182920,"text":"Let's pause for a moment."},{"time":184760,"text":"Is it really possible to build\nan artificial intelligence like that?"},{"time":188680,"text":"Actually, it is."},{"time":190160,"text":"In many ways,"},{"time":191440,"text":"this is a hard engineering problem"},{"time":193440,"text":"with elements of AI,"},{"time":194920,"text":"not some wet hair ball of an AI problem\nthat needs to be engineered."},{"time":199640,"text":"To paraphrase Alan Turing,"},{"time":202320,"text":"I'm not interested\nin building a sentient machine."},{"time":204720,"text":"I'm not building a HAL."},{"time":206320,"text":"All I'm after is a simple brain,"},{"time":208760,"text":"something that offers\nthe illusion of intelligence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":213000,"text":"The art and the science of computing\nhave come a long way"},{"time":216160,"text":"since HAL was onscreen,"},{"time":217680,"text":"and I'd imagine if his inventor\nDr. Chandra were here today,"},{"time":220920,"text":"he'd have a whole lot of questions for us."},{"time":223280,"text":"Is it really possible for us"},{"time":225400,"text":"to take a system of millions\nupon millions of devices,"},{"time":229440,"text":"to read in their data streams,"},{"time":230920,"text":"to predict their failures\nand act in advance?"},{"time":233200,"text":"Yes."},{"time":234440,"text":"Can we build systems that converse\nwith humans in natural language?"},{"time":237640,"text":"Yes."},{"time":238880,"text":"Can we build systems\nthat recognize objects, identify emotions,"},{"time":241880,"text":"emote themselves,\nplay games and even read lips?"},{"time":245280,"text":"Yes."},{"time":246520,"text":"Can we build a system that sets goals,"},{"time":248680,"text":"that carries out plans against those goals\nand learns along the way?"},{"time":252320,"text":"Yes."},{"time":253560,"text":"Can we build systems\nthat have a theory of mind?"},{"time":256920,"text":"This we are learning to do."},{"time":258440,"text":"Can we build systems that have\nan ethical and moral foundation?"},{"time":262480,"text":"This we must learn how to do."},{"time":265360,"text":"So let's accept for a moment"},{"time":266760,"text":"that it's possible to build\nsuch an artificial intelligence"},{"time":269680,"text":"for this kind of mission and others."}]},{"cues":[{"time":271840,"text":"The next question\nyou must ask yourself is,"},{"time":274400,"text":"should we fear it?"},{"time":275880,"text":"Now, every new technology"},{"time":277880,"text":"brings with it\nsome measure of trepidation."},{"time":280800,"text":"When we first saw cars,"},{"time":282520,"text":"people lamented that we would see\nthe destruction of the family."},{"time":286560,"text":"When we first saw telephones come in,"},{"time":289280,"text":"people were worried it would destroy\nall civil conversation."},{"time":292200,"text":"At a point in time we saw\nthe written word become pervasive,"},{"time":296160,"text":"people thought we would lose\nour ability to memorize."},{"time":298680,"text":"These things are all true to a degree,"},{"time":300760,"text":"but it's also the case\nthat these technologies"},{"time":303200,"text":"brought to us things\nthat extended the human experience"},{"time":306600,"text":"in some profound ways."}]},{"cues":[{"time":309840,"text":"So let's take this a little further."},{"time":313120,"text":"I do not fear the creation\nof an AI like this,"},{"time":317880,"text":"because it will eventually\nembody some of our values."},{"time":321720,"text":"Consider this: building a cognitive system\nis fundamentally different"},{"time":325240,"text":"than building a traditional\nsoftware-intensive system of the past."},{"time":328560,"text":"We don't program them. We teach them."},{"time":331040,"text":"In order to teach a system\nhow to recognize flowers,"},{"time":333720,"text":"I show it thousands of flowers\nof the kinds I like."},{"time":336760,"text":"In order to teach a system\nhow to play a game --"},{"time":339040,"text":"Well, I would. You would, too."},{"time":342600,"text":"I like flowers. Come on."},{"time":345440,"text":"To teach a system\nhow to play a game like Go,"},{"time":348320,"text":"I'd have it play thousands of games of Go,"},{"time":350400,"text":"but in the process I also teach it"},{"time":352080,"text":"how to discern\na good game from a bad game."},{"time":354520,"text":"If I want to create an artificially\nintelligent legal assistant,"},{"time":358240,"text":"I will teach it some corpus of law"},{"time":360040,"text":"but at the same time I am fusing with it"},{"time":362920,"text":"the sense of mercy and justice\nthat is part of that law."},{"time":366560,"text":"In scientific terms,\nthis is what we call ground truth,"},{"time":369560,"text":"and here's the important point:"},{"time":371600,"text":"in producing these machines,"},{"time":373080,"text":"we are therefore teaching them\na sense of our values."},{"time":376520,"text":"To that end, I trust\nan artificial intelligence"},{"time":379680,"text":"the same, if not more,\nas a human who is well-trained."}]},{"cues":[{"time":384080,"text":"But, you may ask,"},{"time":385320,"text":"what about rogue agents,"},{"time":387960,"text":"some well-funded\nnongovernment organization?"},{"time":391320,"text":"I do not fear an artificial intelligence\nin the hand of a lone wolf."},{"time":395160,"text":"Clearly, we cannot protect ourselves\nagainst all random acts of violence,"},{"time":399720,"text":"but the reality is such a system"},{"time":401880,"text":"requires substantial training\nand subtle training"},{"time":405000,"text":"far beyond the resources of an individual."},{"time":407320,"text":"And furthermore,"},{"time":408560,"text":"it's far more than just injecting\nan internet virus to the world,"},{"time":411840,"text":"where you push a button,\nall of a sudden it's in a million places"},{"time":414960,"text":"and laptops start blowing up\nall over the place."},{"time":417440,"text":"Now, these kinds of substances\nare much larger,"},{"time":420280,"text":"and we'll certainly see them coming."}]},{"cues":[{"time":422520,"text":"Do I fear that such\nan artificial intelligence"},{"time":425600,"text":"might threaten all of humanity?"},{"time":428280,"text":"If you look at movies\nsuch as \"The Matrix,\" \"Metropolis,\""},{"time":432680,"text":"\"The Terminator,\"\nshows such as \"Westworld,\""},{"time":435880,"text":"they all speak of this kind of fear."},{"time":438040,"text":"Indeed, in the book \"Superintelligence\"\nby the philosopher Nick Bostrom,"},{"time":442360,"text":"he picks up on this theme"},{"time":443920,"text":"and observes that a superintelligence\nmight not only be dangerous,"},{"time":447960,"text":"it could represent an existential threat\nto all of humanity."},{"time":451840,"text":"Dr. Bostrom's basic argument"},{"time":454080,"text":"is that such systems will eventually"},{"time":456840,"text":"have such an insatiable\nthirst for information"},{"time":460120,"text":"that they will perhaps learn how to learn"},{"time":463040,"text":"and eventually discover\nthat they may have goals"},{"time":465680,"text":"that are contrary to human needs."},{"time":468000,"text":"Dr. Bostrom has a number of followers."},{"time":469880,"text":"He is supported by people\nsuch as Elon Musk and Stephen Hawking."},{"time":474880,"text":"With all due respect"},{"time":478160,"text":"to these brilliant minds,"},{"time":480200,"text":"I believe that they\nare fundamentally wrong."},{"time":482480,"text":"Now, there are a lot of pieces\nof Dr. Bostrom's argument to unpack,"},{"time":485680,"text":"and I don't have time to unpack them all,"},{"time":487840,"text":"but very briefly, consider this:"},{"time":490560,"text":"super knowing is very different\nthan super doing."},{"time":494320,"text":"HAL was a threat to the Discovery crew"},{"time":496240,"text":"only insofar as HAL commanded\nall aspects of the Discovery."},{"time":500680,"text":"So it would have to be\nwith a superintelligence."},{"time":503200,"text":"It would have to have dominion\nover all of our world."},{"time":505720,"text":"This is the stuff of Skynet\nfrom the movie \"The Terminator\""},{"time":508560,"text":"in which we had a superintelligence"},{"time":510440,"text":"that commanded human will,"},{"time":511840,"text":"that directed every device\nthat was in every corner of the world."},{"time":515720,"text":"Practically speaking,"},{"time":517200,"text":"it ain't gonna happen."},{"time":519320,"text":"We are not building AIs\nthat control the weather,"},{"time":522400,"text":"that direct the tides,"},{"time":523760,"text":"that command us\ncapricious, chaotic humans."},{"time":527160,"text":"And furthermore, if such\nan artificial intelligence existed,"},{"time":531080,"text":"it would have to compete\nwith human economies,"},{"time":534040,"text":"and thereby compete for resources with us."},{"time":537200,"text":"And in the end --"},{"time":538440,"text":"don't tell Siri this --"},{"time":540440,"text":"we can always unplug them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":541840,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":545360,"text":"We are on an incredible journey"},{"time":547840,"text":"of coevolution with our machines."},{"time":550360,"text":"The humans we are today"},{"time":552880,"text":"are not the humans we will be then."},{"time":555440,"text":"To worry now about the rise\nof a superintelligence"},{"time":558600,"text":"is in many ways a dangerous distraction"},{"time":561680,"text":"because the rise of computing itself"},{"time":564040,"text":"brings to us a number\nof human and societal issues"},{"time":567080,"text":"to which we must now attend."},{"time":569360,"text":"How shall I best organize society"},{"time":572200,"text":"when the need for human labor diminishes?"},{"time":574560,"text":"How can I bring understanding\nand education throughout the globe"},{"time":578400,"text":"and still respect our differences?"},{"time":580200,"text":"How might I extend and enhance human life\nthrough cognitive healthcare?"},{"time":584480,"text":"How might I use computing"},{"time":587360,"text":"to help take us to the stars?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":589760,"text":"And that's the exciting thing."},{"time":592400,"text":"The opportunities to use computing"},{"time":594760,"text":"to advance the human experience"},{"time":596320,"text":"are within our reach,"},{"time":597760,"text":"here and now,"},{"time":599640,"text":"and we are just beginning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":602280,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":603520,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}